race.description: Dubbo City & Gilgandra Toyota Mdn Showcase Plate
race.comment: CASINO DIVA (6) ran a decent race when fresh from a spell two back. Settled at the tail and failed to come on last time over 1300m at Dubbo. Raced once over the mile last prep and scored so she can improve sharply out to this more suitable journey. SUNDAY (12) is still a maiden but her best figures this prep suggest she is in contention. Best run was two back when fourth after leading over 1500m at Hawkesbury. Worth an investment at generous odds. PRINCE OF PROPHETS (2) stormed home but just missed over this distance at Dubbo last start. In fine form and looks a serious contender. HAMMOON SENSATION (4) lightly raced gelding who progressed nicely last start with a win by a nose over 1400m at Dubbo. Can go on with it.
